{"tid":1639847,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港保險業協會個聲明有誤導成分","createTime":"2019-10-08T17:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T02:22:28.000Z","uid":36175,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"29b53d0fa318086c411b79244ff747691a8cdd73","tid":1639847,"uid":36175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJ6sN9n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJ6sN9n.jpg&h=cbfe760d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n視乎個別保單條款，呢句嘢根本就有心誤導人。除咗人壽，危疾，跟本大部分standard 嘅insurance policy 都唔包革命，起義。我唔知佢點介定，不過用緊急法都唔算嘅話咁我都唔知幾時先算。<br />\n<br />\n上AXA 個網睇，搵咗幾種保險，革命，起義，都係不受保範圍。<br />\n<br />\n車保:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MD2r3Jo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMD2r3Jo.jpg&h=41268953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫療:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/az4ug52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faz4ug52.jpg&h=cce8fd7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n意外:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gpBHB6x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgpBHB6x.jpg&h=0e58d890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n商鋪:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jUKJ50v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjUKJ50v.jpg&h=a0332624&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔熟保險條款, 只係求其上網搵，亦無check 其他保險公司，有錯請指證。"},{"pid":"22efc1de365e0839cc2c921c0ae97c8ad41962e5","tid":1639847,"uid":36175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:02:29.000Z","msg":"或者請專業嘅巴絲幫手睇睇"},{"pid":"3344a15d46c03cadf8c0e87122ae6f9f0ccb512e","tid":1639847,"uid":42213,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:11:46.000Z","msg":"無錯 佢既意思即係叫你睇返自己份單既terms"},{"pid":"643fd73418ccd6350223786883215a5faf00007c","tid":1639847,"uid":25133,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:39:48.000Z","msg":"佢既意